OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FIndia salon fined $271,000 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffor 'botching' model's     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fhaircut                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A consumer court in India has ordered a
OL,6, salon to pay 20m rupees ($271,000;     
OL,7, #197,000) in damages to a model for    
OL,8, giving her the wrong haircut.          
OL,10,FIt said the woman used to get jobs from
OL,11,Fhair product firms because of her long 
OL,12,Fhair.                                  
OL,14,FBut the salon chopped her hair short   
OL,15,Fagainst her instructions, causing her a
OL,16,Fhuge loss, the consumer court noted.   
OL,18,FThe salon, which is part of a prominent
OL,19,Fhotel chain in Delhi, is allowed to    
OL,20,Fappeal against the verdict.            
OL,23,D]G     From the BBC News Website       
